OL,4,Cafter nearly 30 years in space
OL,6,FIt collected data on Earth's
OL,7,Fdiminishing polar ice, changing land
OL,8,Fsurfaces, rising sea levels, warming
OL,9,Foceans, and atmospheric chemistry.
OL,11,FIn addition, the ERS-2 was called upon
OL,12,Fto monitor natural disasters, such as
OL,13,Fsevere floods and earthquakes, in
OL,14,Fremote parts of the world.
